---
title: Turkey & Sage Tetrazzini with Sweet Peas, Mushrooms, and Parmesan Cream Sauce
description: First served in 1908, turkey tetrazzini has become a mainstay of American comfort food. The dish is most known for its decadent cream sauce, but our version doesn’t leave you over-stuffed thanks to cream cheese. Earthy sage and thyme bring depth to this savory classic.
